daudio - dynamic sound
====================
daudio is a volume control & sink select ui for dwm.


Requirements
------------
In order to build daudio you need the Xlib header files.


Installation
------------
Edit config.mk to match your local setup (daudio is installed into
the /usr/local namespace by default).

Afterwards enter the following command to build and install daudio
(if necessary as root):

    make clean install


Running daudio
-------------
See the man page for details.
